3.0

Hybrid Jeep is NOT a thing!

December 22, 2022
By Detroit Jeep from Royal oak, Mi
Owns this car

I am a proud Jeep owner for at least 15 years. While I understand Hybrids are different in general, this should not contain the Jeep brand at all. Im still adjusting to the lack of power from my overland. But I can say, when this lease is up this jeep is gone. It is not the Jeep for me, so if you are used to the power of a real Jeep dont buy it! :)
